<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Welcome to MOUAU ClassMate</title>
  <style>
    body { 
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; 
      line-height: 1.6; 
      color: #374151; 
      max-width: 600px; 
      margin: 0 auto; 
      padding: 20px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0fdf4 0%, #f0fdf4 50%, #f8fafc 100%);
    }
    
    .container {
      background: white;
      border-radius: 16px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
      border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    }
    
    .header { 
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #15803d 0%, #16a34a 100%);
      color: white; 
      padding: 40px 30px; 
      text-align: center;
      position: relative;
    }
    
    .header::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      height: 4px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #15803d, #FFF600, #15803d);
    }
    
    .logo { 
      font-size: 28px; 
      font-weight: bold; 
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    }
    
    .logo-subtitle {
      font-size: 14px;
      opacity: 0.9;
      font-weight: normal;
      margin-top: 5px;
    }
    
    .content { 
      padding: 40px 30px; 
    }
    
    .welcome-section {
      background: #f0fdf4;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      border-left: 4px solid #16a34a;
      margin-bottom: 25px;
      position: relative;
    }
    
    .welcome-section::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      right: 0;
      width: 4px;
      height: 100%;
      background: #FFF600;
      border-radius: 0 12px 12px 0;
    }
    
    .button { 
      display: inline-block; 
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #16a34a 0%, #22c55e 100%);
      color: white; 
      padding: 14px 35px; 
      text-decoration: none; 
      border-radius: 8px; 
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 16px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.25);
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    
    .button::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: -100%;
      width: 100%;
      height: 3px;
      background: #FFF600;
      transition: left 0.3s ease;
    }
    
    .button:hover::before {
      left: 0;
    }
    
    .button:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.35);
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #22c55e 0%, #16a34a 100%);
    }
    
    .footer { 
      text-align: center; 
      margin-top: 40px; 
      padding-top: 30px;
      border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      font-size: 13px; 
      color: #6b7280; 
    }
    
    .user-name {
      color: #15803d;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    
    .feature {
      background: #f8fafc;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 15px 0;
      border-radius: 12px;
      border-left: 4px solid #16a34a;
      border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      position: relative;
    }
    
    .feature::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      right: 0;
      width: 4px;
      height: 100%;
      background: #FFF600;
      border-radius: 0 12px 12px 0;
    }
    
    .feature strong {
      color: #15803d;
      font-size: 16px;
    }
    
    .features-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 15px;
      margin: 25px 0;
    }
    
    @media (min-width: 480px) {
      .features-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      }
    }
    
    .celebration-badge {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #15803d 0%, #16a34a 100%);
      color: white;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 500;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    
    .celebration-badge::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 3px;
      background: #FFF600;
    }
    
    .highlight {
      color: #15803d;
      font-weight: 600;
      position: relative;
      display: inline-block;
    }
    
    .highlight::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 2px;
      background: #FFF600;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <div class="logo">MOUAU ClassMate</div>
      <div class="logo-subtitle">Your Academic Partner</div>
      <h1 style="margin: 20px 0 0 0; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 600;">Welcome Aboard!</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
      <div class="welcome-section">
        <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 16px;">Hello <span class="user-name">{{name}}</span>,</p>
        <p style="margin: 10px 0 0 0; font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280;">Congratulations! Your account has been <span class="highlight">successfully verified</span> and is now ready to use.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="celebration-badge">
        üéâ Your Academic Journey Starts Now!
      </div>
      
      <p>You now have full access to MOUAU ClassMate's comprehensive academic platform. Here's what you can do:</p>
      
      <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="feature">
          <strong>üìö Course Materials</strong><br>
          Access lectures, assignments, and learning resources for all your enrolled courses.
        </div>
        
        <div class="feature">
          <strong>üìù Assignment Management</strong><br>
          Submit coursework and track deadlines with our organized submission system.
        </div>
        
        <div class="feature">
          <strong>üìä Progress Tracking</strong><br>
          Monitor your academic performance and grades in real-time dashboard.
        </div>
        
        <div class="feature">
          <strong>üíº Academic Portfolio</strong><br>
          Showcase your projects, research, and academic achievements.
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div style="text-align: center; margin: 35px 0;">
        <a href="{{loginLink}}" class="button">
          Access Your Dashboard
        </a>
      </div>
      
      <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280; text-align: center;">
        Ready to excel in your <span class="highlight">academic journey</span>? Start exploring your dashboard now!
      </p>
      
      <div class="footer">
        <p style="margin: 0 0 10px 0;">
          <strong>MOUAU ClassMate Team</strong><br>
          Student Management System
        </p>
        <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 12px; opacity: 0.8;">
          This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.<br>
          For assistance, contact our support team through the ClassMate portal.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>